org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.system

Class Assert

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.system.Assert

  • public class Assert
extends java.lang.Object
    Assert is a utility class for assertions that generates an exception which gets written to the log, but then continues on with the application. The write to the log gives us notices that something is amiss that needs addressing, but continuing with the app might, for example, allow a robot to continue on in a match rather than aborting in the middle, depending on the nature of the failure.
